		<title>Mayo Clinic installs first magnetic nanoparticle hyperthermia system for cancer research in the US</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-installs-first-magnetic-nanoparticle-hyperthermia-system-for-cancer-research-in-the-us/
		
